      "writtenOn": "2019-05-13T07:58:20Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Hmm, this is interesting. IIUC openssh client resolves the remote addr on the remote system, and it\u0027s usually more convenient (e.g. if the target host is reachable and resolvable only by the remote host). Is it difficult to support the same behavior as openssh client?",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 34,
        "startChar": 57,
        "endLine": 35,
        "endChar": 57
      },
      "revId": "2985495c1b4b16f35570162a62725eb1f130e397",
