      "writtenOn": "2019-05-14T03:28:56Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Hm, ssh.Client.Dial sounds better to me. The method is to connect to a foreign host, not to accept connections right? Then IIUC setting a local address is usually not necessary (unless there are multiple NICs attached to the remote system and want to explicitly select one).",
